@startuml Researcher Accesses SOC Data for Model Training
title **Use Case: Agronomic Model Calibration**\nPoint Blue researcher accesses Caney Fork SOC data to train a predictive model

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #424242
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #9E9E9E
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #F9A825
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #1565C0
skinparam sequenceDividerBackgroundColor #E8F5E9

actor "Dr. Martinez\n(Point Blue researcher)" as Researcher #E8F5E9
participant "Point Blue\nCatalogue UI" as UI #E3F2FD
participant "Point Blue\nEDC Connector" as PB_EDC #E3F2FD
participant "Governance\nKeycloak" as KC #F3E5F5
participant "Caney Fork\nEDC Connector" as CF_EDC #E8F5E9

== Authentication ==

Researcher -> UI : Opens catalogue, clicks "Login"
UI -> KC : OIDC redirect
KC --> Researcher : Login page
Researcher -> KC : Authenticates with Point Blue credentials
note right of KC
  Keycloak issues token with claims:
  **glcdi_membership**: "active"
  **glcdi_participant_type**: "researcher"
  **glcdi_certification_status**: "not-applicable"
end note
KC --> UI : Access token + ID token

== Catalog Discovery ==

Researcher -> UI : Browses available data offers
UI -> PB_EDC : Request Caney Fork catalog\n(DSP catalog request)
PB_EDC -> CF_EDC : DSP Catalog Query\n(includes Point Blue identity token)

group Access Policy Evaluation [on Caney Fork connector]
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : Evaluate **researchers-only** policy\nfor SOC measurements asset
  note right of CF_EDC
    Checks token claims:
    1. glcdi_membership == "active" ? **YES**
    2. glcdi_participant_type in\n   ["researcher","data-steward"] ? **YES**
    => **VISIBLE** in catalog
  end note

  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : Evaluate **members-only** policy\nfor grazing rotation asset
  note right of CF_EDC
    Checks token claims:
    1. glcdi_membership == "active" ? **YES**
    => **VISIBLE** in catalog
  end note
end

CF_EDC --> PB_EDC : Catalog response\n(SOC measurements + grazing rotation\n+ paddock boundaries + NDVI)
PB_EDC --> UI : Display available offers

Researcher -> UI : Selects "SOC Measurements"\nReviews contract terms

note over UI
  Contract terms displayed:
  - Purpose: Model Training or Ecosystem Calibration only
  - Time limit: Until 2026-09-30
  - **Must anonymise** farm-identifiable data
  - **Must attribute** data source in publications
  - Raw data redistribution: **prohibited**
  - Commercial use: **prohibited**
end note

== Contract Negotiation ==

Researcher -> UI : Accepts terms, declares\npurpose = "AgronomicModelTraining"
UI -> PB_EDC : Initiate contract negotiation
PB_EDC -> CF_EDC : DSP Contract Negotiation\n(offer with purpose claim)

group Contract Policy Evaluation [on Caney Fork connector]
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : Evaluate **model-calibration-terms**
  note right of CF_EDC
    Checks offer claims:
    1. purpose in ["AgronomicModelTraining",\n   "EcosystemModelCalibration"] ? **YES**
    2. dateTime <= 2026-09-30 ? **YES**
    => **NEGOTIATION ACCEPTED**
  end note
end

CF_EDC --> PB_EDC : Contract Agreement (FINALIZED)
PB_EDC --> UI : Contract confirmed

== Data Transfer ==

Researcher -> UI : Initiates data transfer
UI -> PB_EDC : Start transfer request
PB_EDC -> CF_EDC : DSP Transfer Request
CF_EDC --> PB_EDC : SOC measurements dataset
PB_EDC --> UI : Transfer complete

note over Researcher
  Dr. Martinez can now use the data
  to train the SOC prediction model.

  **Obligations to fulfill:**
  - Anonymise ranch name & GPS before processing
  - Cite "Caney Fork Farms via GLCDI Data Space"
  - Do not redistribute raw data
  - Do not use for commercial purposes
  - Delete data after prototype phase ends
end note

@enduml
